body:
Ported: https://github.com/algorand/py-algorand-sdk/pull/283

Example call:
```rust
let req = create_dryrun(algod, &signed_txs).await?;
let res = algod.dryrun_teal(&req).await?;
for tx in res.txns {
    println!("{}", app_trace(&tx)?);
}
```

Output:
<img width="662" alt="Screenshot 2022-04-14 at 22 15 11" src="https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1381744/163468641-ee43001e-2cd0-4798-adb0-5d838c1fc28d.png">

